## GroupKind v1 meta

Group        | Version     | Kind
------------ | ---------- | -----------
meta | v1 | GroupKind



GroupKind specifies a Group and a Kind, but does not force a version.  This is useful for identifying concepts during lookup stages without having partially valid types
